{
  "stem": "22979.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, you know, what I learned later how they got [NON-ENGLISH] the-- the-- the-- how you say it?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The dynamite.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know the girls from the union factory?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, a long time, they were smuggling in little, tiny things-- the-- the gun [? power ?] to the sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The sonderkommando had no kitchen for itself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had to bring in the food from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when they bring in the food, they got in contact with other people because the sonderkommando had to pick up the food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Besides this, like I mentioned, Erik Kolka, he was a plumber.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And many times, he had to repair something there too.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I don't know if he smuggled too or not.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But the four girls on January-- I don't know which-- beginning of January, before the death march-- they caught them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They interrogated the girls who worked in the powder room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, Laura Shelly has a book about that, That was her-- that is her last book.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She-- there I read the whole story how it happened, how the gun powder was smuggled in to the sonderkommando, and how it was.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The four girls were hung.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They hung them.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the whole story how the-- they worked-- how you say the term of-- of it, you know, behind-- in-- in Birkenau-- the Resistance.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were the Resistance [? where ?] people whom nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And me, personal, I never knew even about the Resistance.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "First of all, I was so separated from the rest of the inmates.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I somehow was not involved in anything like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The only thing what we smuggled little papers to the Germans-- 'Watch out, Achtung.' You know, Jewish clothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
